        "text": "12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "after that",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] So R.V., R.V. marg. ‘",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "because that",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "’. The purpose of the passage is to account for the destruction of the Temple and the captivity of God’s people. The conjunction is not temporal, but causal: ‘for this reason, namely, that &c.’ The rendering of the R.V. margin is preferable.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "provoked … unto wrath",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The word used here for ‘provoke’ is found in the Hebrew books with this meaning only in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Job 12:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Elsewhere to ‘shake’, ‘disquiet’, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Samuel 28:15",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Isaiah 13:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Isaiah 23:11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
